      {
        "experiment_id": 1,
        "reaction_type": "催化热解反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Pyrolysis reaction",
        "description": "在CDS5250热解器中进行纤维素催化快速热解实验，使用SAPO型催化剂（如ZrCu-18），温度范围为400-800°C，反应时间15秒，产物通过GC-MS分析。",
        "text_snippet": "The pyrolysis experiment was carried out in a CDS5250 pyrolyzer... For cellulose fast pyrolysis, the cellulose was packed between two layers of quartz wool and put into a quartz sample tube... For catalytic pyrolysis experiments, a mixture of cellulose and catalyst (physically mixed) were added as feedstock into the quartz sample tube... The reaction time (solid residence time) and pyrolysis temperature (set point of the furnace) were 15s and 600°C (when considering the influence of temperature, the set temperature were 400°C, 500°C, 600°C, 700°C and 800°C), respectively.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Pyrolysis reaction"
      },
      {
        "experiment_id": 2,
        "reaction_type": "催化热解反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Pyrolysis reaction",
        "description": "在相同操作条件下热解左旋葡聚糖（LG），以研究其在ZrCu-18催化剂作用下的裂解行为及其对呋喃化合物形成的影响。",
        "text_snippet": "To reveal the cracking properties of LG in the presence of ZrCu-18 and understand its (the cracking of LG) effect on other products, LG was pyrolysed under the same operating conditions as cellulose... The addition of ZrCu-18 promotes the cracking of LG, and results in the formation of several sugars... and furan compounds including 2-MF, 3(2H)-furanone and FF.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Pyrolysis reaction"
      }
    ]
  },
